Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: New bonds deal for NY finances
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03z97px
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 2 Nov 1975
New Yorkers vent anger at Ford's refusal of federal bail-out for bankrupt city. New bonds issue under discussion. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less